---
Build a telemetry-only simulator proof receipt from normalized snapshots

Usage: wheelctl moza simulator-telemetry-proof [OPTIONS] --lane <LANE> --game <GAME> --recorder-artifact <RECORDER_ARTIFACT> --duration-ms <DURATION_MS>

Options:
      --json
          Output in JSON format for machine parsing
      --lane <LANE>
          Lane artifact directory, e.g. ci/hardware/moza-r5/2026-05-06
      --game <GAME>
          Simulator or bridge name
  -v, --verbose...
          Verbose logging
      --telemetry-source <TELEMETRY_SOURCE>
          Telemetry source: real_game or simhub_bridge [default: simhub_bridge]
      --recorder-artifact <RECORDER_ARTIFACT>
          Lane-relative normalized telemetry recording artifact
      --duration-ms <DURATION_MS>
          Recording duration in milliseconds
      --json-out <JSON_OUT>
          Write the simulator telemetry proof receipt to this JSON file
      --overwrite
          Replace an existing proof receipt
  -h, --help
          Print help
